  "summary": "A group of Iran-based cyber actors, associated with the Government of Iran (GOI), continues to exploit U.S. and foreign organizations across several sectors. They have been observed collaborating directly with ransomware affiliates to enable encryption operations in exchange for a percentage of the ransom payments. The FBI assesses that these actors do not disclose their Iran-based location to their ransomware affiliate contacts and are intentionally vague as to their nationality and origin.",
